text.tspan: Based on the expert estimates and index by V-Dem , weighted by countries' populations. It captures to which
extent political leaders are elected under comprehensive voting rights in free and fair elections, and freedoms
of association and expression are guaranteed. It ranges from 0 to 1 (most democratic)
